@base = https://mal.sep4.eduardfekete.com
@base2 = http://api.sep4.eduardfekete.com

### Hello
GET {{base}}/
Accept: application/json

### DB check
GET {{base}}/db-check
Accept: application/json

### Collect labeled sensor data
GET {{base}}/collect-data
Accept: application/json

### Model info
GET {{base}}/model-info
Accept: application/json

### Predict a focus rating from temperature
POST {{base}}/predict
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "currentTemperature": 22,
  "maxTemp": 24,
  "minTemp": 20,
  "meanTemp": 22
}

### Invalid prediction payload returns 422
POST {{base}}/predict
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "currentTemperature": 22,
  "maxTemp": 19,
  "minTemp": 20,
  "meanTemp": 22
}

